; Program jumps to jump markers (GOTOB, GOTOF, GOTO, GOTOC)
N10 R1=30 R2=10 R4=3
N20 GOTOF MIDDLE ; jump toward the end of the program, skipping N30
N30 X=999
N40 REPEAT_HERE: X=R1 ; jump label, execution resumes here
N50 R1=R1+R2 R4=R4-1
N60 IF R4>0 GOTOB REPEAT_HERE ; conditional jump toward the beginning
N70 GOTOF 90 ; block numbers are valid jump destinations too
N80 X=999
N90 GOTOC NOWHERE ; destination missing: alarm suppressed, fall through
N100 GOTO FINISH ; searches forward first, then backward
N110 X=999
N120 FINISH: M30
MIDDLE: Y=1
GOTOB REPEAT_HERE
